{"tid":443964,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"普通話真係好燃難聽","createTime":"2017-10-22T06:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T06:21:25.000Z","uid":126320,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"453ad34d11986a27c4afeb091578ef0559a01035","tid":443964,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:03:24.000Z","msg":"今日係酒樓食飯, 隔離嗰兩個大陸人講野大聲又難聽,又加埋啲胡話捲舌音,根本就係啲 野蠻民族先用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國自满州韃虜满語入侵,土共,之後文化方面已經無得救,宋明之風不再<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n計我話普通話加上捲舌音等於全球最難聽語言。滿式漢語勁難聽,傳統香港話最好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正皮:無錯普通話難聽到要帶耳塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮:普通話好燃正,係你唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e9c8a70980bbebff35a85c7920a6e6a4d23ac0","tid":443964,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"尤其係啲蝗仔<br />\n把聲尖普通話又鐘意懶係朗誦腔調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4da8d93ee4b9f99004a1d2f89cbc4ab79094c197","tid":443964,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:20:39.000Z","msg":"計我話根本就係噪音污染,大家一齊向環保署施壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d604d0b1660658f980af00d5faf0c47dd67f16","tid":443964,"uid":66679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}